LatticeTranslator - Class in wlv.mt.xmlwrap
LatticeTranslator transforms an ibm word lattice into an fst in a format required by OpenFST.
It creates a subfolder with the same name as the input file and within the subfolder produces both a .fst file and a list of input symbols (isysms.txt) and a list of output symbols (osysms.txt) for each word lattice
